  <summary>3/8/2005--Introduced.
Stars on Cars Act of 2005 - Amends the Automobile Information Disclosure Act to require manufacturers to include Government safety ratings information on new automobile labels or to note the absence of such ratings. Requires the Secretary of Transportation to prescribe regulations implementing the new labeling requirements.</summary>
